This directory will hold demonstration programs that illustrate how
the new pattern matching features of BCPL can be used. These programs
will be edited versions of demostration programs originally
implemented in the MCPL.

The programs in directory untestedare currently under development.

The programs in this derectory seem to work. Thes programs are;

coins.b
fib.b
splay.b
match.b
turing.b
triangle.b

